re are not many.\n         </div>\n         <div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\">\n          Rosa has always dedicated themselves to the soul and body to the feminist struggle, teaching that in life there are no obstacles and that, in case they were, it falls away naturally.\n         </div>\n         <div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\">\n          For her there were no prohibitions.\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\" style=\"font-family: inherit; margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">\n         <div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\">\n          Rosa will miss a lot and we will always bring it to our heart, between a procession, a garrison and a national assembly.\n         </div>\n         <div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\">\n          Rosa will be with us on the streets of Milan also this March 8.\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\" style=\"font-family: inherit; margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">\n         <div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\">\n          We hold in a big hug to the family.\n         </div>\n         <div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\">\n          Have a nice sister trip!\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </span>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div style=\"clear: both;\">\n </div>\n</div>\n", "description": "The partner Rosa Calderazzi has long been sick, with short moments of improvement. From 24/2 she was hospitalized at S. Raffaele and q ...", "author": [], "source": "https://femminismorivoluzionario.blogspot.com/2024/03/un-saluto-pugno-chiuso-alla-compagna.html"}